race.comment: HEYOKA (6) is a consistent conveyance who has hit the top-five in nine of her past ten starts and rarely puts in a poor one. Boasts a win around this circuit and will be cherry-ripe now fourth-up from the spell. Rates the testing material. ONE BEAT NO BEAT (10) is having her first run for the Vandyke barn and maps ideally from gate three. Respect any push in betting. FREELAND (5) has hit a purple patch of late with two wins and a second from her past three outings. Hard to knock mares in form. IMPOSANT (1) has been plying her trade in harder Group 3 company and will appreciate the drop back in grade here. Expect sharp improvement. OCEAN ALPS (2) strips fitter second-up and may earn some minor money.
